<br>
Invis and run past the infamous bridge over the lava river, take the farthest right tunnel (The one that leads to broodmother PH in Luggald factory).<br>
<br>
The tunnel that slants down has a single Luggald abomination that walks up and down the tunnel.  You can sit at tunnel bottom, root/snare/nuke/kite him up and down the tunnel till he is dead.  Sit on boulder and med.  Rinse/repeat.  Hearts are semi rare but drop off him every now and then, highest heart drop rate Ive seen on any mob in Nadox.<br>
<br>
Note: A named can pop in his place.  Its rare and the loot is Bleh, but the fight is tough (very resistant to snare/root).  Have abscond memmed is you are &lt; 60.<br>
<br>
